---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mantras - Visions on the Path">
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Mantras</h1>
            <p>Short, potent phrases to center awareness. Begin with breath, repeat softly, and let the resonance settle into stillness.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-grid">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>So-Ham</h2>
            <p>"I am That" - Synchronize with the breath. Inhale "So," exhale "Ham." Let the rhythm guide you inward.</p>
            <p class="card-meta">Foundation practice for breath awareness</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Om Shanti</h2>
            <p>Peace invocation. Repeat with intention, allowing each syllable to dissolve tension and invite tranquility.</p>
            <p class="card-meta">Calming and centering</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Om Namah Shivaya</h2>
            <p>Honoring the transformative consciousness within. A classical mantra for inner purification and awakening.</p>
            <p class="card-meta">Advanced practice</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Gayatri Mantra</h2>
            <p>Ancient invocation of divine illumination. Chant to invoke clarity, wisdom, and spiritual light.</p>
            <p class="card-meta">Sacred Vedic mantra</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
